    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This mirrored metal fragment is bolted or welded to the face of the affixed shield. When you Activate it, you attempt to reflect the triggering spell back at its caster with *spell riposte*, using your Athletics modifier for the counteract check. The talisman\u2019s counteract rank is 7th.",
